ok so im in a weird mood. actually... crazy as it is im in a wonderful mood. i got woken up at 8:00 by my very best friends phone call (yeahhhhhhhh!) and then he had to go eat... so he called back later... so i got to be woken by him twice. (he lives in sd i live in ak) so i was supper siked! we decided we are going to get an apartment together in California when we graduate. he says the cutest things... like how when were in cali. hes going to be SOO happy it maks me estatic to hear it. i just wish I could go back home. but i can't... not yet and soon i will have a home. I'm also having a Halooween party. Which will be the first "bigish" party i will have ever had!!!!! (i wish destiny could come :( but oh well) any who im gonna go but i hope the noone that reads this loves it. what ever bla bla bla tootals
KC
